Global DNA Genetic Testing Market Insights
DNA Genetic Testing Market size was valued at USD 4.1 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 9.9 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.1% from 2024 to 2030.

DNA Genetic Testing Market Overview
The global DNA genetic testing market is valued at approximately USD 17.2 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 38.1 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.0% from 2023 to 2030. The rapid advancements in genetic research, increasing demand for personalized medicine, and the growing awareness about genetic disorders are major factors driving the market. With technological advancements and the reduction in genetic testing costs, more individuals and healthcare providers are adopting DNA testing for health, ancestry, and disease prediction purposes. The market is also experiencing increased adoption from direct-to-consumer (DTC) testing services, which are driving revenue growth worldwide.

